OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy with further showers at first
OL,7,Fthis evening, some heavy. These
OL,8,Fshowers turning lighter and more
OL,9,Fscattered through the evening before
OL,10,Fmore rain returns to the Central Belt
OL,11,Fovernight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FRather cloudy morning with
OL,14,Frain. Brighter spells and scattered
OL,15,Fshowers in the afternoon, some turning
OL,16,Fheavy at times. Winds will be mainly
OL,17,Flight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
