OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBrighter
OL,6,Fwith sunny intervals and a few showers
OL,7,Fon Friday. Rain spreading from west on
OL,8,FSaturday, turning heavy in west.
OL,9,FBright intervals and occasional rain
OL,10,Fon Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
